text: Clock Knot is an outdoor painted steel sculpture by Mark di Suvero, installed on the University of Texas at Austin campus, in Austin, Texas, United States. The approximately sculpture was installed along Dean Keeton Street in 2007. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Outdoor sculptures in Austin, Texas Category:Steel sculptures in Texas Category:University of Texas at Austin campus Category:Works by Mark di Suvero
